sequenceDiagram
    %% COMP370 Mini Project 2 - Sequence: Client Request (Normal, Bhupinder Branch)
    autonumber
    participant G as GUI
    participant M as Monitor
    participant C as Client
    participant N1 as Node 1
    participant N2 as Node 2
    participant L as Leader Node
    participant F as Follower Node

    G->>M: connectAndStartLeaderPolling(nodeCount)
    M->>C: discoverLeader()
    C->>N1: GET_LEADER
    N1-->>C: ClientResponse(success=true, leaderId=null)
    C->>N2: GET_LEADER
    N2-->>C: ClientResponse(success=true, leaderId=L)
    M-->>G: update("CLIENT_CONNECTED:L")

    G->>M: sendRequest(command)
    M->>C: sendRequest(command)
    C->>L: PROCESS_JOB(command)
    L->>L: handleClientConnection(request)
    L->>L: appendAsLeader(command)
    L-->>C: ClientResponse(success=true, message="Job accepted by leader...")
    C-->>M: return success message
    M-->>G: response string

    Note over L,F: Replication happens in the leader heartbeat cycle
    L->>L: sendHeartbeats()
    L->>F: AppendEntriesArgs(term, leaderId, prevLogIndex, prevLogTerm, entries, leaderCommit)
    F->>F: handleAppendEntries(args)
    F-->>L: AppendEntriesResults(term, success=true)
    L->>L: handleAppendEntriesResult(...)
    L->>L: updateCommitIndex()

    Note over L: Committed entries are applied in the main loop
    L->>L: apply committed log entry to state machine
